00:33:52,289 --> 00:33:54,290
and temporarily withdraws
from the sport.

780
00:33:54,325 --> 00:33:55,425
Hypothetically.

781
00:33:55,459 --> 00:33:57,260
Hypothetically.

782
00:33:57,294 --> 00:34:00,563
I'll get a warrant, check
Colabro's office for steroids.

