00:34:11,208 --> 00:34:13,576
Brian quit the swim team,
said he injured his shoulder.

789
00:34:13,611 --> 00:34:16,646
No swim team, no drug testing.
Mm-hmm.

790
00:34:16,680 --> 00:34:18,648
So I checked Lanie's report
on the steroids

791
00:34:18,682 --> 00:34:20,450
against the file I got from Vice.

792
00:34:20,484 --> 00:34:23,353
They intercepted a shipment
of similar steroids

793
00:34:23,387 --> 00:34:26,823
that came to New York from a lab in Romania.
So let's look into Brian's life,

794
00:34:26,857 --> 00:34:29,259
see if there's any connection
to Romania.

795
00:34:29,293 --> 00:34:31,461
If we can find a connect,
then hopefully we'll be able

796
00:34:31,495 --> 00:34:33,630
to find Zack's killer.
Kate, you ready?

797
00:34:33,664 --> 00:34:36,299
Yeah. Um, let me
just go get my purse.

798
00:34:36,333 --> 00:34:38,301
You guys are going out
again tonight?

799
00:34:38,335 --> 00:34:40,303
What can I say?
She's a wealth of information.

800
00:34:40,337 --> 00:34:42,305
You are lucky to have her.

801
00:34:42,339 --> 00:34:44,474
Yeah. Yeah, I am.

