810
00:35:01,358 --> 00:35:03,226
(laughs) Yeah.
Yeah, they are.

811
00:35:03,260 --> 00:35:06,162
Ah, well.
If you're unavailable...

812
00:35:06,196 --> 00:35:08,131
(Whispering)
Three, two, one.

