00:35:08,165 --> 00:35:09,632
Well, wait, wait, wait.

814
00:35:09,667 --> 00:35:11,901
Bingo.

815
00:35:11,936 --> 00:35:14,470
Hang on a second.

816
00:35:14,505 --> 00:35:17,440
