00:35:38,629 --> 00:35:40,430
Oh.
That's the rule.

827
00:35:40,464 --> 00:35:44,033
We lose a member,
nobody sits there for a year.

828
00:35:45,603 --> 00:35:47,337
Okay.

829
00:35:47,371 --> 00:35:49,038
Sorry.

830
00:35:49,073 --> 00:35:52,442
So we were just talking about
our books becoming movies.

831
00:35:52,476 --> 00:35:54,110
Michael had "Lincoln Lawyer,"

832
00:35:54,144 --> 00:35:57,180
I had "Shutter Island,"
Ricky has "Heat Wave."

