852
00:36:45,095 --> 00:36:46,238
You know, Dennis is right.

853
00:36:46,358 --> 00:36:48,571
Aside from Brian, who has
the most to lose

854
00:36:48,691 --> 00:36:50,238
if this steroid use gets out?

855
00:36:53,604 --> 00:36:56,039
You know,
I think I might just know.

856
00:37:02,380 --> 00:37:03,965
This is ridiculous.

857
00:37:04,085 --> 00:37:06,398
I was in my apartment
in faculty housing that night.

858
00:37:06,518 --> 00:37:07,546
You could just ask around.

859
00:37:07,666 --> 00:37:09,336
We know you were
in your apartment that night.

860
00:37:09,456 --> 00:37:12,027
Okay. So then why am I here?
Do you know what this is, coach?

