00:39:40,598 --> 00:39:43,000
(Scoffs)
This is ridiculous.

920
00:39:43,034 --> 00:39:45,002
Why would I kill Zack?

921
00:39:45,036 --> 00:39:47,571
Because when Zack found steroids
in Brian's car,

922
00:39:47,605 --> 00:39:49,606
he was conflicted
about what to do.

923
00:39:49,641 --> 00:39:51,241
So he sought counsel

924
00:39:51,276 --> 00:39:53,744
from the one guy
he knew he could trust...

925
00:39:53,778 --> 00:39:56,725
Captain America,
chest full of medals,

926
00:39:56,845 --> 00:39:58,081
guy on the cereal box.

927
00:39:58,116 --> 00:40:01,518
Only you realized,
coach Rome had given Brian

928
00:40:01,553 --> 00:40:03,264
the same steroids
